  "title": "Service Crew",
  "description": "<p>This role entails providing support to the floor team to deliver guests and members a wonderful dining experience. </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>KEY OBJECTIVES &amp; DELIVERABLES</strong></p>\n<p>● Setting up the floor during opening and closing procedures</p>\n<p>● Guiding and training part time staff in their duties and responsibilities as floor commis</p>\n<p>● Maintaining the condiment stations</p>\n<p>● Maintaining the MEP polishing stations</p>\n<p>● Setting up the kitchen pass and manning the food running shifts</p>\n<p>● Setting up each service station with the necessary cutleries/glassware that it needs to run the operation and continually replenishing side stations</p>\n<p>● Delivering food and drinks to tables</p>\n<p>● Supporting the captains with station maintenance, clearing and resetting tables and mise en place for service</p>\n<p>● Supporting reservations with seating shifts</p>\n<p>● Managing laundry inventory and check in/out of deliveries for service</p>\n<p>● Follow club’s policies, procedures and service standards</p>",
