    "description": "<p><strong>Introducing Mandala Club (formally known as the Straits Clan)<br>\n</strong>An inclusively curated community for people who inspire a room.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>At Mandala Club, our core belief is that if you surround yourself with great people, in a great environment, then great things will happen.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>The Mandala Group is a collective of entrepreneurial visionaries crafting next-gen luxury hospitality and property development. &nbsp;We aim to excel in design, architecture, food and service – with an emphasis on equality, not subservience. We balance head with heart, and brains with a playful spirit. We tread with a light foot and we challenge the status quo. We go beyond to surprise and delight everyone we touch.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Under the management of The Mandala Group, the Club will offer dining, working, drinking spaces and, health and wellness facilities. It will also create and curate exciting and inspirational events on a regular basis. The location is a gorgeous around 30,000 sq ft heritage building in Chinatown.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Find out more about us at www.mandala.global</p>",
